OL,3,CDenmark bans extremely hot noodles
OL,4,Cused in TikTok spice challenge
OL,6,FThe Danish government has banned
OL,7,Fseveral flavours of spicy instant
OL,8,Fnoodles due to the risk of "acute
OL,9,Fpoisoning" in children.
OL,11,FThe country's food agency warned
OL,12,Fyoungsters are being drawn to the
OL,13,Fbrand, produced by company Samyan, by
OL,14,Fa TikTok trend challenging them to
OL,15,Ftake on the extreme levels of spice.
OL,17,FThe recalled products include three
OL,18,Fdifferent variants of "hot chicken"
OL,19,Fnoodles - including Buldak 3 x Spicy &
OL,20,FHot Chicken, Buldak 2 x Spicy & Hot
OL,21,FChicken and Buldak Hot Chicken Stew.
