OL,3,CDenmark bans extremely hot noodles
OL,4,Cused in TikTok spice challenge
OL,6,FThe sauce packet which comes with the
OL,7,Fnoodles contains capsaicin, a compound
OL,8,Ffound in chilli peppers.
OL,10,FThe Danish Veterinary and Food
OL,11,FAdministration said the levels of
OL,12,Fcapsaicin in some of Samyan's products
OL,13,Fpose a health hazard.
OL,15,FIt claimed several children in Germany
OL,16,Fhave been hospitalised after eating
OL,17,Fcrisps containing high levels of the
OL,18,Fcompound - and said the levels found
OL,19,Fin the three Samyan products are even
OL,20,Fhigher.
