OL,3,CDenmark bans extremely hot noodles
OL,4,Cused in TikTok spice challenge
OL,6,FThe administration's Head of Unit
OL,7,FHenrik Dammand Nielsen said: "Chilli
OL,8,Fin large quantities poses a risk to
OL,9,Fchildren and frail adults in
OL,10,Fparticular.
OL,12,F"Possible symptoms include burning and
OL,13,Fdiscomfort, nausea, vomiting and high
OL,14,Fblood pressure. That is why we are now
OL,15,Fdemanding that the shops remove the
OL,16,Fproducts from their shelves."
OL,18,FThe products were assessed after a
OL,19,FDanish consumer approached the
OL,20,Fcountry's food agency and questioned
OL,21,Fwhether the noodles should be legal.
