OL,3,CDenmark bans extremely hot noodles
OL,4,Cused in TikTok spice challenge
OL,6,FSale of the instant noodles has now
OL,7,Fbeen banned in the country, and people
OL,8,Fare being encouraged to throw them
OL,9,Faway or bring them back to retailers.
OL,11,FIn a statement to BBC News, a Samyang
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "We understand that
OL,13,Fthe Danish food authority recalled the
OL,14,Fproducts, not because of a problem in
OL,15,Ftheir quality but because they were
OL,16,Ftoo spicy."
OL,18,F"The products are being exported
OL,19,Fglobally. But this is the first time
OL,20,Fthey have been recalled for the above
OL,21,Freason."
